name: Number of Leads signed till September 2022
query:
SELECT SUM(leads.total_leads) as "Number Of Leads Signed Till September 2022:Int:400" 
FROM (
    SELECT
        COUNT(*) as total_leads
    FROM
    	`tabLeed`
    WHERE
        ifnull(signed_at, '') != '' AND
        signed_at < "2022-09-01 00:00:00"
    GROUP BY
    	signed_at
	) leads;
report_name: Number of Leads signed till September 2022
